Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:22.22,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:28.10,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:37.29,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:44.13,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:52.95,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:01:00.18,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:07.59,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:14.72,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:24.21,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
