Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:53.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain is silvery…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a Japanese camping song?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don’t you know it, Eri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:59.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true. Don’t be fooled, Sawachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:02.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Our camping ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we’re really in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:13.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The air must be so fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:15.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Sara could have seen this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:17.98,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:21.22,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the cottage we’ll be staying in tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:18.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,420)}It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,420)}This trip was planned at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:24.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,420)}But does a tea club ordinarily go camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.62,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s where we’ll cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,420)}It’s for training of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.89,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.29,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,420)}But it’s not purely a tea club outing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.58,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:34.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We came because you said there weren’t\Nenough people with only you and Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Hanai-senpai unable to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I gave him a fake date for the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Suou went camping with\NYakumo-kun and the others this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You tricked me, Takano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do until our part-time job starts…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Harima! Let me use your bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, four-eyes, that’s how\Nyou ask for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:05.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It’s like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:11.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Omigosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:16.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my big chance to see if\Nwhat Tenma-chan said is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How can you leave me behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:36.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takano-senpai, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:48.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yakumo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:11.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave all the cooking to us, and the\Nwomen are free to enjoy themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:12.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori, get the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima, gather firewood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if he knows a lot about animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:37.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A delinquent gathering firewood…\NSomething’s wrong, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:45.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten— Tsukamoto-san’s younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:47.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:52.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Tenma-chan, for you!\NShe taught her sister well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the worst, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Tenma-chan say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her younger sister might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he doesn’t remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my special secret curry spice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:20.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just buy the roux at the\Nconvenience store at the foot of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:25.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Yakumo-kun has to taste\Nthe best curry in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of the curry, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, know where Yakumo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She went to help gather firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’re you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:40.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for asking, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, was your older sister\Nangry about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, did she say that somebody\Nwas “the worst,” or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:57.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she did say she talked\Nto Suou-san and Sawachika-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:02.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did she talk to them about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was about a man…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:07.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What sort of man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With a beard… and sunglasses…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The resemblance is coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:21.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did she say about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:26.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She wondered why he practiced\Nconfessing his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn’t understand\Nhis feelings, she said sadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can’t be…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No… but… That could lead\Nto only one conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Namely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:43.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan realized that when I practiced\Nmy confession of love on the trip…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,it was actually what I felt for her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the worst, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what she really said was…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the worst, Harima-kun. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s what she meant to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all because I jumped to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Tenma-chan would\Nnever say I was the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know my own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t read his mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know he’s a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we’d better be heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell your sister\Nwhat we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t remember, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk about animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s kind of… a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and by the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rice balls were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:52.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong? Let’s go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t expect things to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn’t satisfied with\Njust Eri-chan and Miko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s even trying to hit on Yakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s lost all sense of decency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a player, Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:18.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to… I’ve got to protect Yakumo!
