Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Late! You’re late, Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Yakumo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Beardy…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… I just came back from working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this spoiled blonde!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s still mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:50.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was to blame. If I’m not careful,\Nshe’ll tell Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t like that kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only take so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:05.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:06.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:26.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo! Forget him! He’s an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him! I saw Harima-kun hitting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes were dead serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was wearing sunglasses.\NAnd he doesn’t seem like a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t understand men, at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But how could you?\NYou’ve never dated, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven’t either, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:52.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan’s looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:02.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,See that oily, disgusting face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s totally after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only wanted to talk to him—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t know anything about men, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Harima is a player, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All men have those periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it such a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:27.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to talk to Karasuma-san,\Nyou seem to be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s because Karasuma-kun isn’t a player!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:36.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just said all men are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hopeless! I can’t beat Yakumo\Nwhen it comes to logic…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can’t give up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:49.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to protect Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I’m her big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I’ll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.30,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,0)\pos(262,365)}No arguing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:08.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, just do as I say! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wanted to talk to him about animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:18.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s been a while since she’s\Nused “Big Sister Power.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:24.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:27.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten… Tsukamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:39.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you to be my partner\Nin tonight’s scavenger hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight me, one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:47.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this finally be Tenma-chan’s\Nconfession of her love for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:50.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:55.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.65,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord1.5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnj.d.\pos(318,433)}The mask hides his sappy-looking grin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:04.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,At last… At last it’s done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:08.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo! I made my secret curry spices!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hanai, you took too long,\Nso we started without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:15.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m surprised you managed to\Nbring frozen curry here, Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tea club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! After-dinner coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Very thoughtful, Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I ground the beans up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:32.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh-perked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tea club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Imadori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to drink Tenma-chan’s fresh coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky I came!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:56.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s so into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:00.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,These beans must be some sort of sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love beans, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re drawing straws to find our\Npartners for the scavenger hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord1\be1\shad1\fs40\fnAirstream\c&HF1F7FF&\3c&H010344&\pos(500,79)}Mokkori
