Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s time for the scavenger hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:19.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back a charm from a\Nsmall shrine along the forest path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re really going\Nall out, aren’t we? {taken from wf subs}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tea club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,First team up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you trembling, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try anything, and you’ll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll catch up to you soon, Yakumo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:54.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:06.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, I’m sure you know\Nwe’re paired up on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t run or hide from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. Let’s settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I’ll finally settle\Nthis with Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:28.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means… we’ll connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:38.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t expect this rain.\NI wonder if everybody’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve gotta find shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:46.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell him to stay away\Nfrom Yakumo, too, but now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tsukamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re tall, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:15:00.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! I was able to jump over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, we’ll have to\Ncall a truce, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:25.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t know there was\Na deserted school here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire. Warm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s turned into a big mess,\Nhasn’t it? I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay. Don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mustn’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t hope for a better scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:03.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:08.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, when a girl falls in love…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She can only see that person in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:16.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you’re a truly sweet person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:23.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But a girl wants her love\Nto be sweet to only her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just can’t date two girls at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be a player!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t have to tell me that, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the only one in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why, but this\Nis really getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:57.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan will catch cold like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s gotta take off those wet clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:01.37,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp3\fs40\b1\c&H5459E0&\3c&H565852&\bord1\fnCartonsix NC\pos(252,46)\clip(m 232 47 l 386 49 386 0 309 3 300 14 294 22 275 23 263 25 252 29 241 34)}Mwahahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.87,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp3\fs40\b1\c&H5459E0&\3c&H565852&\bord1\fnCartonsix NC\pos(252,46)}Mwahahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I suggest it, she’ll think I’m a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:09.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this girl’s pretty dense, so she\Nwon’t catch on to a casual hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:13.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get her to strip\Nwithout appearing like a creep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You strip, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:43.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you don’t think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:48.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right! He’s serious!\NThat’s how he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:53.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He even made a pass at me\Nand caused me a lot of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s awful! I’m stopping him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be silly. Even Tenma has\Nenough sense to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll just punch him one! That Beard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How’s this? They’re pretty thick,\Nso ain’t they warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,These school curtains…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s kind of embarrassing, but it’s better than catching cold, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You still can’t trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Harima…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:41.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s the girl that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Why, it’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit snickering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I can’t understand you.\NSpeak clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they little kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:05.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsu… ka… mo… to Ten… ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? I can’t hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Okay, I’ll sit next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She means…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:26.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s awfully embarrassing\Nfor a girl to say, “I love you.”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say it first.
