Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.65,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H007BFA&\bord0\b0\fnImpact\pos(327,322)}Passion Unleashed\N{\fsp3\fnArial\fs14\b1}OUT OF CONTROL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Harima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Running out of firewood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it’s gonna get a lot hotter\Nin here, so wait a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s make it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:49.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make firewood out of this wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thing. A cloth to burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:56.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this? Something’s caught on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. Big mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But tonight, I am fearless and invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Harima?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. Maybe we should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the rain’s stopped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eavesdropping is wrong, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven punished you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:46.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid! Let’s go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:54.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Imadori-kun outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of things happened. All kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He won’t get up for a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll let him sleep some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:19.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Yakumo-kun?\NHasn’t Yakumo-kun come back yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:32.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:37.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… we got wet in the rain… and um…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got extra clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tea club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:54.29,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:22:00.05,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:04.75,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:10.22,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.84,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:17.51,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:20.90,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.75,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:28.19,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.33,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.52,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:40.53,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:44.54,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:49.45,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:50.43,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:08.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation’s ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to play some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on School Rumble:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,About three parts.
